{"tid":1635024,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"速食餐點再進化！上班族沒時間吃飯　日本研發「喝的飯糰」","createTime":"2019-10-07T11:27:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T13:45:38.000Z","uid":32511,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ea97bd5771e55f85f1a90cc01d2768037a4556bf","tid":1635024,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:27:05.000Z","msg":"真的是顛覆大家想像，日本上班族常工作一忙就忘記用餐，為了讓他們能快速攝取營養，日本業者竟然突發奇想開發用「喝」的飯糰和咖哩，到底要怎麼喝，帶您一起來看看。<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/10/07/2171545-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F10%2F07%2F2171545-XXL.jpg&h=61679ae4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n看似真空包裝的能量果凍，上頭卻有飯糰的模樣，打開來喝更讓人驚艷，原來這是日本廠商突發奇想所推出「用喝的飯糰」。<br />\n <br />\n日本消費者：「很像白米有真實感，這是飯糰啊。」<br />\n <br />\n看準日本上班族常一忙錯過用餐時間，廠商特別研發喝的「飯糰」。<br />\n <br />\n像是果凍的黏稠食物就是「喝飯糰」的原型，仔細一看還能發現一粒粒米飯，原來開發業者為了保存飯糰口感，真的把米粒放到真空包裝內，再把梅子和鰹魚海苔兩種口味做成膠狀果凍，混在米飯內上班族通勤空檔，隨手一吸就有飽足感。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/10/07/2171567-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F10%2F07%2F2171567-XXL.jpg&h=ed00b130&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n開發廠商負責人豬谷清吾：「我們有聽到很多消費者說，喝起來就像吃飯糰，而且味道很像可以很開心的吃，真的很棒」<br />\n <br />\n還有這個像是易開罐咖啡的飲料，其實也是「喝」的食物，可以喝的蕃茄咖哩。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/10/07/2171623-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F10%2F07%2F2171623-XXL.jpg&h=52dec502&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「喝咖哩」開發小組成員大森規子：「有了它就可以用喝咖啡的感覺用餐。」<br />\n <br />\n可別以為廠商只是把咖哩變成液體飲料，裡頭還有煮透的絞肉和蔬菜，口感獨特，限量推出立刻銷售一空。<br />\n <br />\n廠商接下來也開始研發有點辣的「泰國喝咖哩」，繼續挑戰大家對喝食物的想像。"},{"pid":"7efb117001ef390a5aa38fe46d7a614aee422647","tid":1635024,"uid":30453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:27:25.000Z","msg":"We are temporarily using live channel直播台as english channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634498\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634498</a><br />\n<br />\n[國際戰線] 連登開左英文台！English Channel is LIVE now on LIHKG!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634824\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634824</a>"},{"pid":"62589a73e3932034b0b2ab0670c44226f97b344f","tid":1635024,"uid":306610,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:34:30.000Z","msg":"慘撚到甘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dff34aad246ef60e8c9246b41a8d341bbf0fa9e","tid":1635024,"uid":1703,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:35:28.000Z","msg":"本末倒置 做野係為左要食飯<br />\n唔食飯不如咪撚做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b10557e4c6c210e814b486cc389c93d0412fd076","tid":1635024,"uid":49136,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:38:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rZ1Hr2x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrZ1Hr2x.png&h=7e3e2f6c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7d6dad0ff99be76d308d98c2183aa6fe4e273a89","tid":1635024,"uid":11067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:54:35.000Z","msg":"嘔吐物"},{"pid":"1b524ebae7fa87c570bd32a0c75e5b89a0ec53a6","tid":1635024,"uid":30837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:56:27.000Z","msg":"我屋企隻旺財都唔撚食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcd3a0280171e9207fc425848fd370ea9920ba3f","tid":1635024,"uid":301989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:58:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b720f5d7ca7dd28d28b3cecad3074bfb3ea66aa","tid":1635024,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:01:43.000Z","msg":"直接食能量棒加水動樂都得啦